"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-kids-2024-0722-1461212-say-bonjour-to-the-paris-2024-olympic-and-paralympic-mascots\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The Olympic and Paralympic Games are serious business for the elite athletes taking part, but for the fans it will be an amazing, awesome and fun celebration of sport.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games take place every four years and each time we meet a new mascot!\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Paris 2024, it's time to say hello to The Phryges.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999832003824, \"rank\": 1.6799636380357708e-08, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are inspired by the Phrygian hats which are connected to the French Republic and go back even further as a symbol of liberty.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 0.8763579328290023, \"rank\": 0.14108484367967958, \"text\": \"Phrygian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999773763, \"rank\": 2.2659629300083767e-11, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toOlympics.com: \\\"The motto of the Olympic Phryge and Paralympic Phryge is: Alone we go faster, but together we go further, representing the ways in which the mascots, and the people of the world, can make each other better by working side-by-side.\\\"\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Phryges are the latest in a long line of mascots and you can see them all on theofficial Olympics website.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who is your favourite?\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For all the latest news from Paris 2024 click here!\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999832003824, \"rank\": 1.6799636380357708e-08, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want you to getbehind Team Ireland- and keep an eye on RT\\u00c9jr socials too...  Meet all the Team Ireland Olympic athletes.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999998773240079, \"rank\": 1.2226120758171948e-06, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9jr\", \"score\": 0.988101246429927, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9jr\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9jr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9jr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1114, \"